* --exclude /  --exclude-file (prefix)
* not cross filesystem
* verbose mode should have a least 4 different modes:
    * silent: no output but errors
    * report: provide just a line with stats (duration, speed, volume, #files, #buckets)
    * verbose (default): see basic but important information (which file is being migrated)
    * debug: tool debug mode
    * trace: include libdroplet debug mode
* output to a file
* dry-run mode for backup and restore
* local cache, --cache-dir for archive meta information
* rpm/deb
